Kiddwaya’s billionaire father, Terry Waya, has said that the reality television show is a unifying factor. In a recent Instagram live interview with BBC Africa pidgin, he said: “Big Brother Naija house show though I no see anybody wey say this one na my Yoruba brother, na only him I go dey follow do things, this one na my Igbo brother na only him I go follow do things or my Hausa brother or whatever, them con mix them dey do as if na one big family as if dem no know where anybody come from this show good well well e day unite Nigeria well well. I like am well.”